;
BIOMOLECULE: 1
THIS ENTRY CONTAINS THE CRYSTALLOGRAPHIC ASYMMETRIC UNIT
WHICH CONSISTS OF 2 CHAINS. SEE REMARK 350 FOR
INFORMATION ON GENERATING THE BIOLOGICAL MOLECULE(S).
SIZE EXCLUSION CHROMATOGRAPHY SUPPORTS THE ASSIGNMENT
OF A DIMER AS A SIGNIFICANT OLIGOMERIZATION STATE.
;
