SEQUENCE
THIS CONSTRUCT IS COMPRISED OF AMINO ACIDS 81-377 OF THE
FULL-LENGTH PROTEIN (1-377) AND WAS EXPRESSED WITH A
PURIFICATION TAG MGSDKIHHHHHHENLYFQG. THE TAG WAS REMOVED
WITH TEV PROTEASE LEAVING ONLY A GLYCINE FOLLOWED BY THE
TARGET SEQUENCE.
